# Used only by `vite build` (production). In prod the frontend (Pages) and the
# API (Worker) live on different origins, so point the frontend at the Worker.
# Vite inlines VITE_* vars into the build. In dev this file is ignored and
# requests stay relative, proxied to the Worker by vite.config.ts.
VITE_API_URL=https://template-api.jose-enrique-barco.workers.dev
